The paper discusses the vulnerability of neural networks to adversarial attacks, which is a common topic in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method for evaluating representation quality is also relevant to the sub-field of neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the need for robustness against attacks, which is a topic in the sub-field of computer security (cs.CR).
